data.name: infoLabel1.Text
data.value:
TedEncrypt is a file encryption tool. It will encrypt files in the current directory using a generated key.
This key will appear in the current directory and will be used for file decryption.
You should move the key to a secure location, and only move it back to this folder when decrypting.
If the key is deleted, you WILL NOT be able to recover the encrypyted files.
